_sText:
This is NAV-file for [de_contra](http://css.gamebanana.com/maps/15208 "").

Okay, bots using all posible ways now. No exceptions. They go through the channel crossing the map; in the tunnel; on the wall near bombsite A; they jump into the holes in the wall that leads to tunnel and walk freely on the water... Walk freely everywhere! :D

Also, added place names, so bots will tell you where the enemy is, where the bomb, etc. But to avoid confusion in the future, I recommend you to run on a map alone and learn how located the place names, then...

Just have fun ;)

UPDATE 17.08.2014: Accelerated exit of bots from both respawns. Bots getting stuck beside crates on bombsites - fixed. And some minor improvements.
